quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  21,58,"FajaAAalahum juthathan illakabeeran lahum laAAallahum ilayhi yarjiAAoon"
  21,59,"Qaloo man faAAala hatha bi-alihatinainnahu lamina aththalimeen"
  21,60,"Qaloo samiAAna fatan yathkuruhumyuqalu lahu ibraheem"
  21,61,"Qaloo fa/too bihi AAalaaAAyuni annasi laAAallahum yashhadoon"
  21,62,"Qaloo aanta faAAalta hatha bi-alihatinaya ibraheem"
  21,63,"Qala bal faAAalahu kabeeruhum hathafas-aloohum in kanoo yantiqoon"
  21,64,"FarajaAAoo ila anfusihim faqalooinnakum antumu aththalimoon"
  21,65,"Thumma nukisoo AAala ruoosihim laqadAAalimta ma haola-i yantiqoon"
  21,66,"Qala afataAAbudoona min dooni Allahima la yanfaAAukum shay-an wala yadurrukum"
  21,67,"Offin lakum walima taAAbudoona mindooni Allahi afala taAAqiloon"
  21,68,"Qaloo harriqoohu wansurooalihatakum in kuntum faAAileen"
  21,69,"Qulna ya naru kooneebardan wasalaman AAala ibraheem"
  21,70,"Waaradoo bihi kaydan fajaAAalnahumual-akhsareen"
  21,71,"Wanajjaynahu walootan ilaal-ardi allatee barakna feeha lilAAalameen"
  21,72,"Wawahabna lahu ishaqawayaAAqooba nafilatan wakullan jaAAalna saliheen"
